<section id="quality" class="relative z-[2] bg-[var(--paper-2)] border-t border-[var(--rule)] py-12 md:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-[1100px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">

    <!-- Section head -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr] gap-5 md:gap-16 mb-10 md:mb-14 items-end">
      <div>
        <div class="font-[var(--mono)] text-[11px] tracking-[.3em] text-[var(--moss)] uppercase">III &middot; Quality</div>
        <h2 class="font-[var(--display)] font-normal mt-3 mb-0 leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.01em] text-[var(--ink)]"
            style="font-size:clamp(24px,3vw,40px)" data-ko-block>
          측정되지 않는 답은<br/><em class="italic text-[var(--moss)]">맺히지</em> 않습니다
        </h2>
        <h2 class="font-[var(--display)] font-normal mt-3 mb-0 leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.01em] text-[var(--ink)]"
            style="font-size:clamp(24px,3vw,40px)" data-en-block>
          An answer<br/>that <em class="italic text-[var(--moss)]">can't be measured</em><br/>doesn't ripen
        </h2>
      </div>
      <p class="font-[var(--serif)] text-base leading-[1.7] text-[var(--ink-2)] max-w-[560px] m-0" data-ko-block>Gopedia의 모든 변경은 IR(Information Retrieval) 지표로 검증됩니다. 세계수가 흔들릴 때마다 — 우리는 그 흔들림을 측정합니다.</p>
      <p class="font-[var(--serif)] text-base leading-[1.7] text-[var(--ink-2)] max-w-[560px] m-0" data-en-block>Every change to Gopedia is verified by Information Retrieval metrics. Whenever the World Tree shifts — we measure how it shifts.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- IR grid: chart + copy -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 md:gap-14 items-center">

      <!-- Chart -->
      <div id="ir-chart" class="bg-[var(--paper)] border border-[var(--rule)] p-6 md:p-8">
        <div class="font-[var(--display)] italic text-[16px] text-[var(--moss)] mb-5 flex justify-between items-baseline gap-4">
          <span>
            <span data-ko-block>RAG 품질 &middot; v1.4 &rarr; v1.7</span>
            <span data-en-block>RAG quality &middot; v1.4 &rarr; v1.7</span>
          </span>
          <span class="font-[var(--mono)] text-[10.5px] text-[var(--ink-2)] not-italic tracking-[.1em] shrink-0">0 &mdash; 1.0</span>
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-5">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-[90px_1fr_40px] sm:grid-cols-[120px_1fr_48px] gap-2 sm:gap-3.5 items-center">
            <div class="font-[var(--sans)] text-[11.5px] text-[var(--ink-2)]">Recall@10<small class="block text-[10px] tracking-[.12em] text-[var(--bark)] uppercase">v1.4 baseline</small></div>
            <div class="gp-track h-[22px] relative" style="background:repeating-linear-gradient(90deg,transparent 0,transparent 19px,var(--rule-2) 19px,var(--rule-2) 20px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--rule)">
              <div class="gp-fill absolute inset-y-0 left-0 bottom-px w-0 transition-[width] duration-[1400ms] ease-[cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1)]" style="background:var(--bark-2)" data-w="68"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="font-[var(--mono)] text-[12px] text-right" style="color:var(--bark-2)">.68</div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-[90px_1fr_40px] sm:grid-cols-[120px_1fr_48px] gap-2 sm:gap-3.5 items-center">
            <div class="font-[var(--sans)] text-[11.5px] text-[var(--ink-2)]">Recall@10<small class="block text-[10px] tracking-[.12em] text-[var(--bark)] uppercase">v1.7 current</small></div>
            <div class="gp-track h-[22px] relative" style="background:repeating-linear-gradient(90deg,transparent 0,transparent 19px,var(--rule-2) 19px,var(--rule-2) 20px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--rule)">
              <div class="gp-fill absolute inset-y-0 left-0 bottom-px w-0 transition-[width] duration-[1400ms] ease-[cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1)]" style="background:var(--moss)" data-w="89"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="font-[var(--mono)] text-[12px] text-[var(--moss)] text-right">.89</div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-[90px_1fr_40px] sm:grid-cols-[120px_1fr_48px] gap-2 sm:gap-3.5 items-center">
            <div class="font-[var(--sans)] text-[11.5px] text-[var(--ink-2)]">nDCG@10<small class="block text-[10px] tracking-[.12em] text-[var(--bark)] uppercase">v1.4 baseline</small></div>
            <div class="gp-track h-[22px] relative" style="background:repeating-linear-gradient(90deg,transparent 0,transparent 19px,var(--rule-2) 19px,var(--rule-2) 20px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--rule)">
              <div class="gp-fill absolute inset-y-0 left-0 bottom-px w-0 transition-[width] duration-[1400ms] ease-[cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1)]" style="background:var(--bark-2)" data-w="54"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="font-[var(--mono)] text-[12px] text-right" style="color:var(--bark-2)">.54</div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-[90px_1fr_40px] sm:grid-cols-[120px_1fr_48px] gap-2 sm:gap-3.5 items-center">
            <div class="font-[var(--sans)] text-[11.5px] text-[var(--ink-2)]">nDCG@10<small class="block text-[10px] tracking-[.12em] text-[var(--bark)] uppercase">v1.7 current</small></div>
            <div class="gp-track h-[22px] relative" style="background:repeating-linear-gradient(90deg,transparent 0,transparent 19px,var(--rule-2) 19px,var(--rule-2) 20px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--rule)">
              <div class="gp-fill absolute inset-y-0 left-0 bottom-px w-0 transition-[width] duration-[1400ms] ease-[cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1)]" style="background:var(--moss)" data-w="81"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="font-[var(--mono)] text-[12px] text-[var(--moss)] text-right">.81</div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-[90px_1fr_40px] sm:grid-cols-[120px_1fr_48px] gap-2 sm:gap-3.5 items-center">
            <div class="font-[var(--sans)] text-[11.5px] text-[var(--ink-2)]">Faithfulness<small class="block text-[10px] tracking-[.12em] text-[var(--bark)] uppercase">v1.4 baseline</small></div>
            <div class="gp-track h-[22px] relative" style="background:repeating-linear-gradient(90deg,transparent 0,transparent 19px,var(--rule-2) 19px,var(--rule-2) 20px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--rule)">
              <div class="gp-fill absolute inset-y-0 left-0 bottom-px w-0 transition-[width] duration-[1400ms] ease-[cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1)]" style="background:var(--bark-2)" data-w="71"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="font-[var(--mono)] text-[12px] text-right" style="color:var(--bark-2)">.71</div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-[90px_1fr_40px] sm:grid-cols-[120px_1fr_48px] gap-2 sm:gap-3.5 items-center">
            <div class="font-[var(--sans)] text-[11.5px] text-[var(--ink-2)]">Faithfulness<small class="block text-[10px] tracking-[.12em] text-[var(--bark)] uppercase">v1.7 current</small></div>
            <div class="gp-track h-[22px] relative" style="background:repeating-linear-gradient(90deg,transparent 0,transparent 19px,var(--rule-2) 19px,var(--rule-2) 20px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--rule)">
              <div class="gp-fill absolute inset-y-0 left-0 bottom-px w-0 transition-[width] duration-[1400ms] ease-[cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1)]" style="background:var(--moss)" data-w="94"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="font-[var(--mono)] text-[12px] text-[var(--moss)] text-right">.94</div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-[90px_1fr_40px] sm:grid-cols-[120px_1fr_48px] gap-2 sm:gap-3.5 items-center">
            <div class="font-[var(--sans)] text-[11.5px] text-[var(--ink-2)]">
              <span data-ko-block>인용 정확도</span><span data-en-block>Citation acc.</span>
              <small class="block text-[10px] tracking-[.12em] text-[var(--bark)] uppercase">v1.4 baseline</small>
            </div>
            <div class="gp-track h-[22px] relative" style="background:repeating-linear-gradient(90deg,transparent 0,transparent 19px,var(--rule-2) 19px,var(--rule-2) 20px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--rule)">
              <div class="gp-fill absolute inset-y-0 left-0 bottom-px w-0 transition-[width] duration-[1400ms] ease-[cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1)]" style="background:var(--bark-2)" data-w="62"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="font-[var(--mono)] text-[12px] text-right" style="color:var(--bark-2)">.62</div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-[90px_1fr_40px] sm:grid-cols-[120px_1fr_48px] gap-2 sm:gap-3.5 items-center">
            <div class="font-[var(--sans)] text-[11.5px] text-[var(--ink-2)]">
              <span data-ko-block>인용 정확도</span><span data-en-block>Citation acc.</span>
              <small class="block text-[10px] tracking-[.12em] text-[var(--bark)] uppercase">v1.7 current</small>
            </div>
            <div class="gp-track h-[22px] relative" style="background:repeating-linear-gradient(90deg,transparent 0,transparent 19px,var(--rule-2) 19px,var(--rule-2) 20px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--rule)">
              <div class="gp-fill absolute inset-y-0 left-0 bottom-px w-0 transition-[width] duration-[1400ms] ease-[cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.2,1)]" style="background:var(--moss)" data-w="92"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="font-[var(--mono)] text-[12px] text-[var(--moss)] text-right">.92</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Legend -->
        <div class="flex gap-4 mt-5 font-[var(--sans)] text-[11px] text-[var(--ink-2)]">
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <i class="inline-block w-2.5 h-2.5 align-middle not-italic" style="background:var(--bark-2)"></i>
            <span data-ko-block>이전 (v1.4)</span><span data-en-block>previous (v1.4)</span>
          </span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <i class="inline-block w-2.5 h-2.5 align-middle not-italic" style="background:var(--moss)"></i>
            <span data-ko-block>현재 (v1.7)</span><span data-en-block>current (v1.7)</span>
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Copy -->
      <div class="min-w-0">
        <h3 class="font-[var(--display)] font-medium leading-[1.1] mt-0 mb-4 text-[var(--ink)]"
            style="font-size:clamp(20px,2.5vw,30px)" data-ko-block>
          매주 <em class="italic text-[var(--moss)]">1,200건</em>의 질문으로<br/>나무를 흔들어 봅니다.
        </h3>
        <h3 class="font-[var(--display)] font-medium leading-[1.1] mt-0 mb-4 text-[var(--ink)]"
            style="font-size:clamp(20px,2.5vw,30px)" data-en-block>
          We shake the tree<br/>with <em class="italic text-[var(--moss)]">1,200 queries</em><br/>every week.
        </h3>
        <p class="font-[var(--serif)] text-base leading-[1.7] text-[var(--ink-2)]" data-ko-block>Gopedia는 자체 평가 데이터셋(<strong>Gold Set</strong>)을 통해 매 릴리스마다 Recall, nDCG, Faithfulness, Citation Accuracy를 측정합니다. 숫자가 떨어지는 변경은 절대 머지되지 않습니다.</p>
        <p class="font-[var(--serif)] text-base leading-[1.7] text-[var(--ink-2)]" data-en-block>Gopedia maintains its own <strong>Gold Set</strong> evaluation suite — every release is scored on Recall, nDCG, Faithfulness, and Citation Accuracy. A change that drops the numbers never lands.</p>
        <div class="mt-4 font-[var(--mono)] text-[11px] text-[var(--bark)] tracking-[.04em]" data-ko-block>* 내부 한국어 + 영어 1,200쿼리 기준 &middot; 2024-12 측정</div>
        <div class="mt-4 font-[var(--mono)] text-[11px] text-[var(--bark)] tracking-[.04em]" data-en-block>* internal Korean + English 1,200-query set &middot; measured 2024-12</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  const fills = document.querySelectorAll('.gp-fill');
  const io = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach((e) => {
      if (e.isIntersecting) {
        const el = e.target as HTMLElement;
        el.style.width = el.dataset.w + '%';
        io.unobserve(el);
      }
    });
  }, { threshold: 0.3 });
  fills.forEach((f) => io.observe(f));
</script>
